docs.description:
The Questionnaire contains aggregated annual data on Rail, Road, Inland Waterways and Oil Pipelines transport for the following:
I. Infrastructure
II. Transport equipment
III. Enterprises, economic performance and employment
IV. Traffic
V. Transport measurement
(for IV and V there is a certain overlap with legal acts)
Note that, for Oil Pipelines, the only source is the Common Questionnaire. Information concerning the other transport modes can be found in the documentation provided for each relevant domain.
The questionnaire is sent to the competent national authorities that are responsible for the completion. The questionnaire is not supported by any legal acts but is based on a gentlemen's agreement with the Member States and the completeness varies from country to country. The Data for the non EU Member States of the ITF and UNECE are to be found at these organisations.
Full metadata at: http://epp.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/cache/ITY_SDDS/EN/road_eqs_esms.htm
